title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Dec 1 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Dec 1 2021
description:
Fauci reveals first U.S. Omicron case: double vaxxed, mild symptoms in Northern California. Salute and honor 16-year-old hero Tate Myre, who gave his life saving fellow students in Michigan school shooting. WTA pulls tournaments from China. Fauci admits the definition of "fully vaccinated" may change. Update on Buck's scooter stolen in NYC.
